@node "History"

                                    @{b}History@{ub}

2010.04.25   V1.2b   Public release.
                     - Fix invalid cast making hit or crash at copy or delete operation
                     - Fix never deleted objects at copy or delete operation
                     - Minor fix in French translation catalog

2010.04.04   V1.2a   Public release.
                     - Add updated German catalog by otti (Hans-J÷rg Ottinger)
                     - Fix progress bar class destroying hit at program exit

2010.03.31   V1.2    Public release.
                     - Add multi-selection for copying or deleting
                     - Add directory items inclusive or exclusive filter
                     - Add file items inclusive or exclusive filter
                     - Add shortcut button to set filter for a file only comparison
                     - Add button to avoid existing item warning requester to confirm
                     - Add option to count or not file difference as a directory difference
                     - Add user notification when skipping item comparison on read error
                     - Add application icon in the about window
                     - Open new Rival instance on directory double click action
                     - Print file relative name when unable to display file differences
                     - Print "Version not found" when binary file version is not available
                     - Improve file and directory link support
                     - Fix comparison bug for large file names
                     - Fix crash with history display management
                     - Fix second parameter lost bug for user choice requester
                     - Fix crash when compared directories has no file
                     - Use additional process for global comparison
                     - Use additional process for items copying or items deleting
                     - Refactor user interface sources

2006.10.31   V1.1    Public release.
                     - Save compared directory history and restore at starting  
                     - Search and display version for binary files
                     - Integrate progress bar and interrupt button in GUI
                     - Integrate new debug system
                     - Some bugs fixed

2006.05.02   V1.0a   Public release.
                     - Fixed bug: Node opening/closing in tree 2 has not effect
                       on the matching node of the 2 other trees

2006.04.29   V1.0    Public release.
                     - First MorphOS/PPC release

@endnode

